  <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:1rem">Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom:0.75rem">We treat this tribute as a family trust. Contributor email addresses and telephone numbers are private and visible only to administrators.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:0.75rem">We do not publicly display home addresses, private disputes, or sensitive information about minors without approval.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:0.75rem">Family contributions (photos, stories, names, and board posts) are published for the family when a valid family PIN is used. Administrators may still edit or remove content when needed.</p>
  <p style="margin-bottom:0.75rem">You may request correction or removal of content via the links in the footer.</p>
  <p>Original uploaded files are preserved for the family archive. Web-optimized copies are generated for display.</p>
</div></section>
